MathML" display=3D"block"><mi>x</mi></math></mjx-assistive-mml></mjx-contai=
ner>-axis</li>
<li>The volume of water in a bathtub based on the rate of flow from the fau=
cet</li>
<li>The center of mass of a vehicle so that its safety features can be fine=
-tuned</li>
<li>The best way to create a 3D model</li>
</ul>
<p>The more you think about it, the more you=E2=80=99ll start to see all th=
e interesting and important uses of integrals all around you!</p>
