<p><em>What are the two types of integrals?</em></p>
<p>There are several different kinds of integrals, but the two main types a=
re definite and indefinite integrals.</p>
<p><em>Why are integrals used?</em></p>
<p>Integrals are used to find the anti-derivative, or the inverse of the de=
rivative. This unlocks many different pieces of information, like area, vol=
ume, velocity, and more.</p>
